OL,3,C'A shining light': UK's first Asian
OL,4,Cwoman Lord Mayor in the UK dies at age
OL,5,Cof 80
OL,7,FLeicester councillor Manjula Sood MBE,
OL,8,Fwho was the first Asian woman Lord
OL,9,FMayor in the UK, has died at the age
OL,10,Fof 80.
OL,12,FShe represented the ward of
OL,13,FStoneygate, and also held the title of
OL,14,FAssistant City Mayor for Community
OL,15,FCohesion.
OL,17,FShe had recently spent time in London
OL,18,Fwith her grandchildren.
OL,20,F"The void she leaves behind is
OL,21,Fimmeasurable"
