OL,7,FIn a statement to ITV News Central,
OL,8,Fher friend and community leader
OL,9,FSuleman Nagdi, from the Federation of
OL,10,FMuslim Organisations, said:
OL,12,F"It is with profound sadness and a
OL,13,Ftruly heavy heart that I share the
OL,14,Fdevastating news of the passing of our
OL,15,Fbeloved Mrs Manjula Sood.
OL,17,F"To me, she was far more than a local
OL,18,Fcouncillor, community leader ` she was
OL,19,Flike an elder sister, someone I looked
OL,20,Fup to with immense respect and
OL,21,Faffection.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/5
