OL,3,C'A shining light': UK's first Asian
OL,4,Cwoman Lord Mayor in the UK dies at age
OL,5,Cof 80
OL,7,F"Her warmth, her wisdom, and her
OL,8,Fgenerous spirit shaped not only my
OL,9,Flife but the lives of so many in our
OL,10,Fcommunity"
OL,12,F.Mr Nagdi went on to say:
OL,14,F"She was a shining light ` a woman of
OL,15,Fextraordinary compassion, dignity, and
OL,16,Funwavering dedication.
