OL,3,C'A shining light': UK's first Asian
OL,4,Cwoman Lord Mayor in the UK dies at age
OL,5,Cof 80
OL,7,F"Her kindness touched countless
OL,8,Fhearts, and her legacy of selfless
OL,9,Fservice, love, and grace will live on
OL,10,Fin all of us who were fortunate enough
OL,11,Fto know her.
OL,13,F"The void she leaves behind is
OL,14,Fimmeasurable. We have lost a guide, a
OL,15,Fmentor, and a beautiful soul whose
OL,16,Fpresence made the world a kinder place.
