OL,7,F"During this impossibly difficult
OL,8,Ftime, my thoughts are with her family,
OL,9,Fher loved ones, and everyone whose
OL,10,Flife she touched with her remarkable
OL,11,Fspirit.
OL,13,F"Manjula my sister, you will be
OL,14,Fdeeply, deeply missed".
